
                                     BUGS TO BE FIXED
																		 ----------------


==========================================================
BUG 1:

Impossible to interrupt execution of fgldoc with CTRL-C
-------------------------------------------------------

CTRL+C does nothing - fgldoc continues execution


==========================================================
BUG 2:

fgldoc needs an option to stop (or not) on error
------------------------------------------------

Something like -i (ignore) and to stop on error should be defaut.

Now, when for instance, ther is an error in incovation of p4gl from fgldoc,
fgldoc reports the error and continues.

==========================================================
